age is just one way in which the industrial strategy is working to build and support the investment in people. The Government continue to build an economy that works for everyone. Making work pay for the lowest earners in our society is a key part of our commitment. I commend these regulations to the House. Question put and agreed to.     Share           2.52 pm          Committee rose.                    ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
